OL,6,FMore than 130 officers and staff in
OL,7,FBritain's biggest police force,
OL,8,Fincluding two serial rapists,
OL,9,Fcommitted crimes or misconduct after
OL,10,Fthey were not properly vetted, a
OL,11,Freview has found.
OL,13,FDavid Carrick, one of the UK's worst
OL,14,Fsex offenders, and Cliff Mitchell, who
OL,15,Fcarried out a "campaign of rape" on
OL,16,Ftwo victims over nine years, were
OL,17,Famong Metropolitan Police officers who
OL,18,Fwere not properly checked.
