OL,6,FCarrick, who was given 37 life
OL,7,Fsentences for his crimes, was not
OL,8,Fproperly vetted in 2017, with checks
OL,9,Ffailing to reveal an allegation of
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse against him.
OL,12,FMitchell was allowed to join the force
OL,13,Fin 2020 after a vetting panel, which
OL,14,Fpartly aimed to improve diversity,
OL,15,Foverturned a decision to reject him
OL,16,Ffrom the police despite a previous
OL,17,Faccusation of raping a child.
OL,19,FThe 131 cases were revealed as part of
OL,20,Fa vetting review that looked at the 10
OL,21,Fyears up to the end of March 2023.
