OL,6,FOther serious crimes committed by the
OL,7,Fofficers and staff include drug use,
OL,8,Fracism, violence and affray.
OL,10,FThe review published on Thursday found
OL,11,Fthat thousands of police officers and
OL,12,Fstaff were not properly checked amid
OL,13,Fpressure during a national recruitment
OL,14,Fdrive from July 2019 to March 2023.
OL,16,FSenior officers at the Met chose not
OL,17,Fto meet national guidelines amid a
OL,18,Fscramble to find 4,557 recruits in a
OL,19,Fthree-and-a-half year period.
