OL,6,FThe deviations from standard practice
OL,7,Fmeant thousands of references were not
OL,8,Fchecked, and shortcuts in vetting led
OL,9,Fto the recruitment and retention of
OL,10,Fsome officers and staff who should not
OL,11,Fhave been in the force and contributed
OL,12,Fto police-perpetrated harm and damaged
OL,13,Fpublic trust, it said.
OL,15,FThe Home Secretary ordered a watchdog
OL,16,Fto inspect the force's vetting
OL,17,Fprocedures in light of the report.
