OL,6,FThe review said senior officers faced
OL,7,Fpolitical pressure and had to meet
OL,8,Frecruitment targets or lose funding to
OL,9,Fother forces.
OL,11,FSince current Met Commissioner Sir
OL,12,FMark Rowley took over the role in
OL,13,FSeptember 2022, 1,500 officers have
OL,14,Fbeen sacked in what has been billed as
OL,15,Fa bid to clean up the force. He was
OL,16,Falso a high-ranking Met officer
OL,17,Fbetween 2011 and 2018.
