OL,6,FThe report said that out of 730
OL,7,Fvetting cases reviewed, 39 officers
OL,8,Fand staff had to be re-checked, with
OL,9,F23 cleared.
OL,11,FOne officer resigned, another was
OL,12,Fsacked for a different reason, six
OL,13,Fcases are ongoing, and eight have been
OL,14,Freferred to potentially face dismissal.
OL,16,FThe report concluded: "There were
OL,17,Fdeviations from policy and practice,
OL,18,Foverconfidence in the ability to
OL,19,Frecruit at scale and lack of resources
OL,20,Fin vetting increased risk.
